<p data-start="346" data-end="482">The subject is <strong data-start="361" data-end="402"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Ludwig Wittgenstein</span></span></strong> (mentioned here for reference; do not repeat inside the LaTeX unless you wish).</p>
