<p data-start="3599" data-end="3768">a <strong data-start="3601" data-end="3623">transition chapter</strong> showing how this silence eventually forced his return to philosophy in a different mode (therapy, ordinary language, the <em data-start="3745" data-end="3761">Investigations</em>), or</p>
</li>
